data.description: LOWERED BY $44K+ SINCE LIST DATE!! DON'T MISS OUT ON THIS AMAZING OPPORTUNITY! PRIMARTY ON THE MAIN. Beautifully updated two-level home with primary suite, full bath, and laundry room all located on the main floor. This home sits next to a greenspace on a quiet dead-end street. Featuring a large open layout with vaulted ceilings and hardwood floors. Kitchen has updated appliances, pantry, granite countertops and a large pantry. Primary suite with full bath and jetted tub, high ceilings, walk-in closet and a door opening out to the patio. Laundry room on main. New covered concrete patio allowing for year-round use of the well-maintained backyard and entertaining space. RV parking and RV electrical outlet. Plus, so much more! This home is a MUST SEE!!
